{"tid":2024330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解大家唔識得逐個擊破？","createTime":"2020-05-19T14:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T15:43:11.000Z","uid":202095,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"34c6f7a8e984df001289dac9266b0649687e5b6f","tid":2024330,"uid":202095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:12:46.000Z","msg":"你哋成日話抗爭冇方向<br />\n但係其實有好多方向只係政府每日都有柒事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以搞到大家啲注意力唔知擺喺邊度<br />\n方向一多啲人自然唔知向邊度落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然整唔死黑警同林鄭，點解唔直接專注整死一個部門佢呢？<br />\n<br />\n大家唔係好憎楊潤雄嘅咩？<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">咁咪專注一個禮拜鋪天蓋地(po文宣喺IG又或者開po)數臭佢同教畜局囉<br />\n(又或者從佢身邊嘅人落手俾壓力佢)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n之後咪用一個禮拜再做鳩通訊局扼殺言論自由囉<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 大家知唔知可以持續一個禮拜嘅輿論影響力係好大㗎！</span><br />\n一時又通訊局一時又教育局一時又林鄭<br />\n<br />\n而家睇熱門都已經知<br />\n大家已經放低咗楊潤雄想喺香港搞文革。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家可以專注整得死一個局長例如(楊潤雄)，大家咪可以有個明確目標囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2085d2003108c51652a1ffaf9614312807e65084","tid":2024330,"uid":202095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:13:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d04df2cd34ca95629ff9de2ff6b96dd6cd64ada6","tid":2024330,"uid":202095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4bDOLGa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4bDOLGa.jpg&h=dd8a5801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外國讀書嘅垃圾批評香港教育"},{"pid":"58a93b2536c7e68632386f930df8dfb0a3233bd3","tid":2024330,"uid":202095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JDeaY1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJDeaY1k.jpg&h=6b65f591&s={SIZ